      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a suitable project car or a budget-friendly option for someone handy. While it remains functional and gets you from point A to point B, it shows clear signs of its age and mileage, including noticeable wear on the interior upholstery and several visible scratches and dings on the exterior. Mechanically, it is operational but will likely require some maintenance or minor repairs in the near future to keep it running smoothly. It's a solid, honest car for someone looking for basic transportation at an affordable price point.",
