    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior with deep, mirror-finish paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks present. The interior is equally pristine; the premium Nappa leather remains supple and matte, showing zero signs of bolster wear, and the cabin retains its original factory-fresh scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment, never seen inclement weather, and sits on a brand-new set of high-performance tires. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new in every measurable way.",
      "price": 48500.0,
